revision.text: * [[File:Kangaskhan.png|35px]] Kangaskhan (attacking) vs. [[File:Gengar.png|35px]] Gengar (defending) - Kangaskhan is mono normal typed and Gengar is dual ghost-poison typed. Kangaskhan's normal type is 0x effective (immune) against Gengar's ghost type. As this is the only type of Kangaskhan, Kangaskhan's normal type is used. Thus, Kangaskhan's attack against Gengar is 0 as per the type multiplier of 0 (0x).
